text: Anna A. Georges Eshoo ( ; born December 13, 1942) is an American politician. She is the U.S. representative from , since 1993. She is a member of the Democratic Party. She is the only Assyrian American in Congress and one of only two Armenian-American women in Congress. On November 21, 2023, she announced she would not seek re-election in 2024. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from California Category:Politicians from Connecticut Category:People from Atherton, California Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:People from Menlo Park, California Category:20th-century American politicians Category:21st-century American politicians
